{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b1e696ecaf","title":"为《晋绥日报》题写报头","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"944b00baa2","index":0,"year":1948,"month":4,"day":2,"articleId":"b1e696ecaf"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji24","name":"毛泽东全集第24卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji24.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji24":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"10a026a30e","type":"paragraph","text":"为《晋绥日报》题写报头”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"b1e696ecaf"},{"id":"4eff1f4557","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年4月2日）晋绥日报春级款毛泽东为《晋绥日报》题写的报头。1]《晋缓日报》是解放战争时期中共晋级分局的机关报，前身是1940年9月18日创刊的《抗战日报》，1946年7月1日改名，内容主要是社论、际国内新间、地方消息等，宜传中国共产党的政策，指导地方的工作。1948年4月2日，毛泽东曾对该报编辑人员发表《对晋缓日报编辑人员的该话》。1949年5月1日《晋绥日报》停刊。这是1948年4月，毛泽东为《普级日报》题写的报头","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"b1e696ecaf"}],"page":{"id":"5bc52a812f","publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"b1e696ecaf","start":205,"end":205}}}},"__N_SSG":true}